message: "If you use this manuscript, replication package, or Phase 1 toolkit, please cite it as below."
title: "A Public-Data Review-Priority Framework for Medicaid Residential Care Oversight: Evidence from Washington State Adult Family Homes"
type: dataset
authors:
  - family-names: Hussein
    given-names: Mohamed Noor
date-released: 2026-07-06
version: "1.0"
