  - public-data review priority
  - Minnesota Medicaid enforcement record
  - replication package
abstract: >
  A public, journal-safe replication package for a working paper applying a
  20-indicator public-data review-priority typology (derived from Minnesota's
  public Medicaid enforcement record) to Washington State's Adult Family Home
  sector. Includes the manuscript, a de-identified aggregate replication
  dataset, portable analysis scripts, and a static Phase 1 public-data
  review-priority dashboard. This is a review-priority research prototype,
  not a fraud score, validated predictive model, or enforcement tool.
